Title: Shipwrecked
Writer: O.V. Falck-Ytter (book), Nils Gaup (screenplay), Bob Foss (screenplay), Greg Dinner (screenplay), Nick Thiel (screenplay)
Actors: Stian Smestad, Gabriel Byrne, Louisa Milwood-Haigh, Trond Peter Stamsø Munch
Plot: A young Norwegian boy in 1850s England goes to work as a cabin boy and discovers some of his shipmates are actually pirates.
